-> executing the code from the sram:
1) text section in link.ld has to be in RAM ("> RAM" instead of "> FLASH")
2) with the monitor put 0x20000000 in 0xe000ed08 (mww 0x20000000 0xe000ed08)
to tell the NVIC that the vector table is at the beginning of the sram. 
